      • toExpressionEncoded

        public java.lang.String toExpressionEncoded()
                                     throws java.io.UnsupportedEncodingException
        Builds an URL expression for the field constraint.
        This method currently uses textual symbols of operators only.
        The field values are encoded in case of textual values.
        Returns:
        A sting containing partial url path segment
        Throws:
        java.io.UnsupportedEncodingException - unable to encode the url string
